{"tid":1041350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"充滿創意既你入一入黎","createTime":"2019-02-28T18:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T02:14:53.000Z","uid":100909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e803f302a72e95e07e025f834b62319f9a6eab4e","tid":1041350,"uid":100909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"就黎long d完番香港 想比個驚喜男朋友<br />\n有無咩idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n佢知我大概邊幾日會番黎 但唔知exactly邊日咩時間<br />\n但我地每日都會facetime 我覺得好難呃到佢同埋上左機會變單tick facetime又唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗緊好無到時買wifi扮一直都未上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗住一落機番屋企沖個涼就出去佢屋企附近搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我想係發生一啲事令佢自己走出個門口而唔係我好有目的咁叫佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似好難咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a484144379f434042bf8bfe3ca763b769ab67a49","tid":1041350,"uid":208678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:18:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">帽子</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"5aa059c43046ef390811ce105a695ffd0c784ca7","tid":1041350,"uid":100909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a484144379f434042bf8bfe3ca763b769ab67a49","tid":1041350,"uid":208678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:18:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">帽子</span></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:20:19.000Z","msg":"捱左咁耐唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538613673dfbc9b917681a9582d6c489960af4f6","tid":1041350,"uid":236586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:23:52.000Z","msg":"同佢朋友夾埋令佢唔得閒搵